CAREERBUILDER_API_JOB_DESC = "&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline&quot;&gt;Vonage Business is currently looking for Sales\r\nDevelopment Representatives in Atlanta, GA!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;As\r\na member of the business Sales team, the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Development Representative&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is\r\nresponsible for taking a pivotal approach to identifying and qualifying\r\nbusiness opportunities to grow our business. Successful employees are\r\nperformance-driven and demonstrate their ability to be tenacious self-starters\r\nevery day.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Vonage\r\noffers a fast-paced, innovative environment where you will be provided the\r\ntools, resources and outstanding leadership to sell cloud communications to\r\nbusinesses. We offer competitive compensation and benefits as well as the\r\nopportunity to work with a bright, motivated group of individuals who share a\r\ncommon goal. When you step into our office, you&amp;rsquo;ll instantly understand why\r\nVonage is a destination work place. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Recent\r\ncollege graduates with previous sales experience or sales professionals are\r\nencouraged to apply. If you&amp;rsquo;re the type of person who thrives in a fast-paced,\r\nstart-up environment with an inclusive, diverse culture, then you&amp;rsquo;ve landed in\r\nthe right place!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Our Benefits:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Vonage\r\nrecognizes that benefits are an important component of a total compensation\r\npackage. To that end, the company offers a comprehensive benefits program &amp;ndash; one\r\nthat enables employees to select coverage that makes the most sense for their\r\nindividual situation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Medical&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Vision Care&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Prescription Drug Coverage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Dental&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Life and AD&amp;amp;D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Supplemental Life&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Dependent Life&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Short Term Disability&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Long Term Disability&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Supplemental Long Term\r\n    Disability&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Health Care Spending Account&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Dependent Care Spending Account&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Telemedicine Services&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Transportation Spending Account&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;401K Savings Plan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;529 College Saving Plan&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Voluntary Home &amp;amp; Auto\r\n    Insurance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Employee Referral Program&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Several amazing Employee\r\n    Recognition Programs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;Free Gym&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline&quot;&gt;Key\r\nResponsibilities:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Communicating\r\n    with ideal customer profile prospects using a mix of telephone calls, email,\r\n    and other communication mediums.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Create a\r\n    fantastic first impression to prospects with a friendly attitude, compelling\r\n    message, and consistent follow up.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Educate and\r\n    develop leads to turn them into qualified opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Manage and\r\n    track detailed lead, account, contact, opportunity, and sales activity in our\r\n    CRM system.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Meet and\r\n    exceed monthly sales goals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Meet and\r\n    exceed daily activity expectations (calls, emails, total contacts)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Accept\r\n    feedback and training to continue to improve and develop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;"
